txt.en: 'The battle deepens in the Ettenmoors, we need reinforcements.'
'Stand fast and take positions in the field, warriors!'
'Go now, into the field and stand against Angmar's amry!'
'The Free People will stand against this dark tide from the north, go now and fight!'
'Defenders! Our troops need support in the field.'
'To arms, brethren! Our forces need support in the field.'
